description: Request a cost allocation tag backfill. This will backfill the activation status (either active or inactive) for all tag keys from para:BackfillFrom up to the time this request is made. You can request a backfill once every 24 hours.

parameters.name: BackfillFrom
parameters.description: The date you want the backfill to start from. The date can only be a first day of the month (a billing start date). Dates can't precede the previous twelve months, or in the future.

nested_items.name: BackfillRequest
nested_items.description: An object containing detailed metadata of your new backfill request.

nested_items.name: BackfillFrom
nested_items.description: The date the backfill starts from.

nested_items.name: RequestedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the backfill was requested.

nested_items.name: BackfillStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the cost allocation tag backfill request.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the backfill status was last updated.
